      "date": "2025-04-15 13:42:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nIf these tests are only failing in Oleg's test config, then they should not be disabled completely. Otherwise, it is likely that they will not be enabled again for a long time and are likely to pick up failures. The exception should be as limited as possible. \n\nSomething like:\n\n  if [[ $HOSNAME =~ oleg ]]; then\n       always_except ...\n  fi\n\nSame for all of these other patches if they are only related to the Janitor test config.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
